OL,3,CWarning to Whitehall as departments
OL,4,Casked to find lowest priority spending
OL,5,Careas
OL,7,FDepartments have been asked to
OL,8,Fidentify the 20% of spending which is
OL,9,Flowest priority, and some have been
OL,10,Fasked to find as much as 40%, ITV News
OL,11,FDeputy Political Editor Anushka
OL,12,FAsthana reports
OL,14,FA number of senior sources across
OL,15,Fgovernment have told me that they have
OL,16,Fbeen asked to identify the 20% of
OL,17,Fspending within their departments that
OL,18,Fthey see as lowest priority.
OL,20,FOne suggested that they had been asked
OL,21,Fto go even further - up to 40%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
