OL,3,CWarning to Whitehall as departments
OL,4,Casked to find lowest priority spending
OL,5,Careas
OL,7,FThe move - which I revealed on the ITV
OL,8,FNews Talking Politics podcast -
OL,9,Funderlines a series of likely
OL,10,Fdifficult decisions across government
OL,11,Fspending - alongside billions in
OL,12,Fwelfare cuts - in this spring's
OL,13,Fspending review.
OL,15,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,16,Fis drawing up plans to overhaul
OL,17,Fdisability and health benefits to
OL,18,Fsignificantly reduce the number of
OL,19,Fpeople who are judged as unable to
OL,20,Fwork.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
