OL,5,Careas
OL,7,FThat means far fewer disabled people
OL,8,Fwill receive higher benefit levels,
OL,9,Fand many more will be expected to
OL,10,Fsearch for work.
OL,12,FThe changes to disability and health
OL,13,Fbenefits are being put forward in a
OL,14,Fgreen paper which is meant to be a way
OL,15,Fthat a government consults on
OL,16,Fproposals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
