OL,5,Careas
OL,7,FAs such, they were not meant to be
OL,8,Fscored in the spring statement. But
OL,9,FI've heard that's no longer the case -
OL,10,Fsome of the measures will be
OL,11,Fintroduced immediately so the savings
OL,12,Fcan be counted sooner.
OL,14,FThere will also be major changes to
OL,15,FPersonal Independence Payments - which
OL,16,Fare meant to help disabled people pay
OL,17,Ffor the additional costs associated
OL,18,Fwith their disability. The move is
OL,19,Flikely to trigger a major backlash.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
