OL,5,Careas
OL,7,FI can also reveal that the previous
OL,8,FConservative prime minister Rishi
OL,9,FSunak stepped back from means testing
OL,10,FPersonal Independence Payments at the
OL,11,Flast moment after senior advisers
OL,12,Fwarned him that the optics would be
OL,13,Fterrible.
OL,15,FAdvice, including written submissions,
OL,16,Fstressed that any changes would be
OL,17,Fseen as "taking wheelchairs and other
OL,18,Fessential aids" off a million disabled
OL,19,Fpeople.
