OL,7,FOn the suggestion that at least some
OL,8,Fdepartments had to identify 20% low
OL,9,Fpriority spending a Downing Street
OL,10,Fsource said it was certainly true that
OL,11,Fdepartments across government were
OL,12,Fbeing asked to "deprioritise" spending.
OL,14,FThey said that the state had ballooned
OL,15,Fand needed to be tackled.
