OL,7,FOn welfare, Sunak did push ahead with
OL,8,Fchanges to the work capability
OL,9,Fassessment- saying they would save
OL,10,F#3bn.
OL,12,FAdvisers saw them as much more
OL,13,Fpalatable for voters- with polls
OL,14,Fsuggesting people are quite
OL,15,Funsympathetic to those on out of work
OL,16,Fbenefits.
OL,18,FBut his plan was challenged in the
OL,19,Fcourts and judges agreed with
OL,20,Fdisability campaigners that the
OL,21,Fconsultation had been misleading.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
