OL,7,FThe government suggested that the
OL,8,Fmotivation was not to save money but
OL,9,Fget people into work, but the OBR
OL,10,Fpredicted that while over 400,000
OL,11,Fwould lose money, only around 3,000
OL,12,Fwould move into jobs.
OL,14,FLabour accepts the consultation is
OL,15,Fflawed but is pushing ahead with cuts
OL,16,F- and much bigger than those
OL,17,Foriginally mooted.
